STEP settings
  GIVES: threshold: float
  MODE:  exact

STEP load
  TAKES: file: str
  GIVES: items: List<str>
  MODE:  exact

STEP classify
  TAKES: item: str, threshold: float
  GIVES: label: str
  MODE:  exact

FLOW pipeline
  settings()
  -> load(file="in.csv")
  -> FOR EACH item IN items PARALLEL AS labels:
       classify(item=item, threshold=threshold)
